- reservations (RESERVED, IN_USE, RETURNED)

Reservation steps:
1. User finds and reserves an item
– Selects pickup and return dates
– Reservation is created with status: RESERVED
2. User goes to the store on the pickup date
– Brings confirmation
3. Admin verifies the user and updates the reservation status to IN_USE
– Equipment is handed over to the user
4. User returns the item to the store on the return date
– Admin inspects the item and updates the reservation status to RETURNED